Prerequisite:  user is assumed to understand Jenkins extension plugin process and install necessary tool, e.g. maven etc.  Please refer to Jenkins wiki https://wiki.jenkins-ci.org/display/JENKINS/Extend+Jenkins

Build and install steps:

Jians-Mac-Pro:cloudtest jianzhang$ mvn clean
Jians-Mac-Pro:cloudtest jianzhang$ mvn package
Jians-Mac-Pro:cloudtest jianzhang$ cp target/cloudtest.hpi $JENKINS_HOME/plugins/

(Jians-Mac-Pro:build jianzhang$ ant dist-jenkinsplugin-install ) 

restart Jenkins 

FAQ :
1. ProjectBuildingRequest error  
    [exec] Caused by: java.lang.ClassNotFoundException: org.apache.maven.project.ProjectBuildingRequest
    [exec]     at java.net.URLClassLoader$1.run(URLClassLoader.java:202)
    [exec]     at java.security.AccessController.doPrivileged(Native Method)
	...

anwser: Maven need to be upgraded to Maven 3
Jians-Mac-Pro:build jianzhang$ mvn -version
Apache Maven 3.0.3 (r1075438; 2011-02-28 09:31:09-0800)


